    //         id: "basic-demat-account-services-for-you",
    //         title: "Basic Demat account services for you",
    //         content: "<p>If you want to trade in <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>equities</a>, then it is mandatory to have a <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>demat account</a> in your name. Many of us may already be trading in <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>equities</a> and already have a <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>demat account</a> or multiple <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>demat accoun</a>ts. There may be some <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>investors</a>, who may want to invest in the <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>stock market</a>s with a conservative view, and do not want to risk a large sum of money.</p><p>If you have any plans to open a <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>demat account</a> in the near future, or are a conservative investor then it would help to know the nuances of holding a basic service <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>demat account</a> (<a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>BSDA</a>) to your name. A <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>BSDA</a> is a basic option as against the complete <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>demat account</a>, it basically is a <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>no frills account</a>, which is good for <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>investors</a> opting to invest a small sum of money in the <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>stock market</a>s and whose hold small valued portfolios.</p><p>The full form of demat is dematerialized account.  To hold your <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>equities</a> or shares or other financial instruments like <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>mutual funds</a> in a secure electronic format, you need to have a <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>demat account</a> which serves the purpose. In order to buy and sell <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>equities</a> it is mandatory to have a <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>demat account</a>. Securities and Exchange Board of India (<a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>SEBI</a>) is the governing body which has laid down the guidelines and has also mandated all <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>demat service providers</a> to provide <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>BSDA</a> to individual.</p><p>One can open a <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>BSDA</a> with any of the <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>demat service provider</a>s like <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>banks</a> or other <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>financial institutions</a>. There are no charges for opening of a normal <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>demat account</a> or <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>BSDA</a>, however the <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>annual maintenance charges</a> (<a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>AMC</a>) will vary with different providers. You will need to check the <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>AMC</a> with your respective provider. Some institutions may offer complete free services for the first year, but will start charging individuals from the second year onward, so please check with the respective <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>banks</a> and <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>demat service providers</a> on their websites. </p><p><strong>Terms and conditions for opening a <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>BSDA</a>:</strong><li>When your investment horizon is below rupees two lakhs, then you can opt for a <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>BSDA</a></li><li>If your investment value does not exceed rupees fifty thousand then there will be no annual charges levied</li><li>Annual maintenance charge of rupees hundred is applicable if your investment holdings exceed rupees fifty thousand up to rupees two lakhs</li></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> The moment your portfolio value exceeds rupees two lakhs, the normal <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>demat account</a> charges will be applied. The value of your portfolio is calculated at the end of every trading day and the closing prices of the share price or NAV’s are taken into consideration. This amount is then compared against the price slabs mentioned in the above terms and conditions. Based on which slab it falls under you will be charged the respective amount.</p><p>While a <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>BSDA</a> inherits most of the services that a normal <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>demat account</a> has, there are certain services that differ. Let us look at these differences.</p><p><strong><a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>SMS Alerts</a>:</strong> You will receive <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>SMS alerts</a> for each and every transaction that you conduct once you register your mobile number with the demat service provider...</p><p><strong>Charges for Statements:</strong> You can opt for either an electronic statement or a physical statement. If you opt for the electronic version then no charges are applicable for the statements. If you opt for hard copies or physical statements then the service providers have to provide you with two free statements after which they can levy a charge which does not exceed rupees twenty five as mandated by <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>SEBI</a>.</p><p><strong><a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>Annual Statement</a>:</strong> One hard copy of the <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>annual statement</a> is dispatched to the address which the individual has registered with the <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>demat service providers</a>. It can also be sent as a soft copy via email, depending on the option that the individual has chosen at the time of opening the account.</p><p>One can also convert their existing normal <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>demat account</a> into a <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>BSDA</a> from your next cycle of billing; however the condition is that the user should not have any other <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>demat account</a>s in existence. The For details <a href='https://www.<a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' class='link' target='_blank'>sebi</a>.gov.in/media/press-releases/aug-2012/facility-for-a-basic-services-demat-account-bsda-_23308.html' target='_blank'>click here</a> to visit the page on <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>SEBI</a> website.</p><p><a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>BSDA</a> on account of its low maintenance charges makes it easier for <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>investors</a> to invest in shares at the <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>stock market</a>, or the IPO’s, or Gold ETF’s, bonds and other financial instruments.</p>",
