    //         title: "Subscription services by CIBIL",
    //         content: "<div class='blog-content'><p>Credit information bureau India limited (<a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>CIBIL</a>) as it was formerly known, is now known as <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>Trans Union</a> <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>CIBIL</a> or often referred to as TU – <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>CIBIL</a>. This company was founded in the year 2000 and was India’s first <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>CIC</a> (Credit Information Company).</p><p>The purpose of this company is to compute and compile and individuals <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>credit score</a> and provide a ranking based on his payment or <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>repayment history</a> of <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>credit cards</a> and any other <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>loans</a> that they may have taken in the past or any <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>loans</a> or credit card bills that are currently outstanding. <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>Banks</a> and financial lending institution’s send a report on a monthly basis to TU-<a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>CIBIL</a> for the purpose of computation</p><p>Based on the individuals <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>credit score</a> <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>banks</a> or lending institutions may approve or reject a credit card or loan. Hence it is important to have a good TU-<a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>CIBIL</a> score to ensure that your <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>loans</a> and <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>credit cards </a>are approved seamlessly.</p><p>The erstwhile <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>CIBIL</a> used to charge individuals a one-time fee for providing a <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>credit score</a>, every time the individual requested for it. Since the score is dynamic and changes based on the individual’s <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>repayment histor</a>y, there were instances where an individual would get good score say for example in the month of August of any year. Based on this if the individual applied for loan three to four months down the loan, there were chances of it getting rejected as the score may have changed if the individual has defaulted on any payment post the month of August. The individual would then need to re-apply to find out his <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>credit score</a> and once again pay the fee.  This was a cumbersome process and also cost wise it was on the higher side. In order to ease the process TU-<a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>CIBIL</a> has now come up with a subscription model for obtaining and individuals <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>credit score</a> on a regular basis. </p><p><a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>CIBIL</a> currently has three plans for users to choose from as follows:</p><p><li><strong>Plan 1:</strong> Valid for a period of one month. The fees for this is rupees 550/- In the one month duration the user can check for his <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>CIBIL</a> score on a daily basis.</li><li><strong>Plan 2:</strong> Valid for a period of 6 months. The fees for this is rupees 800/- In the six months duration the user can check for his <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>CIBIL</a> score on a daily basis.</li><li><strong>Plan 3:</strong> Valid for a period of 1 year. The fees for this is rupees 800 /-. In the one year duration the user can check for his <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>CIBIL</a> score on a daily basis.</p><p>Apart from the unlimited access to the <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>CIBIL</a> score as per the above plans, the user also gets unlimited access to the following services by <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>CIBIL</a> :</p><p><li><a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>CIBIL</a> score history and <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>CIBIL</a> score analysis</li><li><a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>CIBIL</a> report and <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>CIBIL</a> credit summary</li><li>Custom and tailored loan offers to suit your requirements</li><li>Allows you the facility to file for disagreements on erroneous data. This can be done immediately and is available online.</li></p><p>If you are in the process of obtaining a loan for various reasons like buying a house or car etc. in the near future then it is advisable to opt for the higher plans, based on your time horizon. </p><p>One needs to visit the following link (<a class='link' href='https://myscore.cibil.com/CreditView/chooseSubscription.page?enterprise=CIBIL' target='_blank'>click here</a>) and choose the required plan and follow the online process.</p><p>The pricing of the plans are subject to change, hence one needs to visit the <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>CIBIL</a> website and check for the latest pricing and updates to any policies.</p></div>",
