    //         content: "<div class='blog-content'><p>It is now mandated by the <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>IRDA</a> to link your <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>PAN card</a> or <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>Aadhar card</a> to all the <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>insurance policies</a> that you haver. In the absence of a <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>PAN card</a> an individual can submit <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>Form</a> 60 as compliance for the requirement.</p><p><a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>Insurance policy </a>holders are getting intimations from the respective <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>insurance companies</a>, via SMS, or email, or even offline letters asking them to link their PAN or <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>Aadhar card</a> to the policies. They are providing complete details on how one can complete the process of linking.</p><p>Before you undertake the process of linking it is necessary that you register your mobile number to receive the OPT (one time password) for verification when you provide the <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>Aadhar card</a> or <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>PAN card</a>. </p><p>The most effective and simple way is to do the linking online. If you are already a registered user with the website of the <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>insurance company</a> that you hold a policy for, then the process is quite simple. </p><p><ul><li>Login to the portal of the respective <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>insurance policy</a></li><li>In the boxes provided, please enter the details of your <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>Aadhar card</a> / <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>PAN card</a></li><li>Click on the submit or verify buttons</li><li>You will receive an OTP on the registered mobile number. (This mobile number should be the same number which you have linked your <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>Aadhar card</a> to)</li><li>Your <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>Aadhar car</a>d / <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>PAN car</a>d will get linked once you enter the <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>Aadhar card</a> / <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>PAN card</a> number and click on Submit.</li></ul></p><p>If you have not yet registered on the respective portals of the <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>insurance companies</a>, you will then need to first get yourself registered on the respective portals and then follow the steps above.</p><p>Most of the <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>insurance companies</a> have also created a devoted landing page on their websites for linking your <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>Aadhar card</a> / <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>PAN card</a>. For example: For Star health and allied <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>insurance company</a> you can visit the following link and update the <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>Aadhar Card</a> / <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>PAN card</a> details <a href='https://retail.starhealth.in/updatecustomerdetails' target='_blank' class='link'>https://retail.starhealth.in/updatecustomerdetails</a>. Similarly you can use Google search to find out the landing pages of the respective websites. For example you can type the following in the Google search box: “Link PAN and Aadhar to SBI Life insuance”. You can replace SBI Life insurance with any <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>insurance compan</a>y name that you want.</p><p>You can also complete the formalities offline. You will need a photo copy of your <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>Aadhar card</a> / <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>PAN card</a> and you will need to self-attest the same. With this copy you can visit the nearest branch of your respective <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>insurance company</a> and submit the same to the authorized personnel or officer in the branch. The branch will then link the <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>Aadhar card</a> / <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>PAN card</a> against the policy</p><p><strong>Note:</strong> If your total payment exceeds rupees fifty thousand, then you will need to submit your <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>PAN card</a> or <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>Form</a> 60/61, each time you make the payment</p><p>As of now there is no deadline to do the linking, but we recommend that you do so immediately to ensure that the <a href='http://pehlakadam.in/' target='_blank'>insurance claims</a> are processed smoothly without any hassles.</p></div>",
